{"tid":1099913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌13歲男童遭𠝹傷頸 警拉18歲阿哥","createTime":"2019-04-10T05:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T08:02:02.000Z","uid":3090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff7f9ced3e382b2b84ba3a3305842c9b029ff49d","tid":1099913,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abNtNiA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabNtNiA.png&h=55733a8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逸東邨兩兄弟爭執，13歲弟弟受傷。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n中午12時23分，東涌逸東邨勤逸樓一名13歲男童報警，指稱與18歲胞兄爭執，其間遭對方用刀𠝹傷頸。警員接報到場，由救護車將傷者送院，經初步調查後拘捕其涉案的哥哥。"},{"pid":"4ee7b3f9aa48ae2b4f00af5d8652bba6f3d63540","tid":1099913,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501cacec463526c700eec3627a34095d5fdeeb5f","tid":1099913,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:52:17.000Z","msg":"東涌呢d悲情都市，真係比狗住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d267b55be47e910cfe03dba6d5a947900aade6b9","tid":1099913,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:57:01.000Z","msg":"公屋兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76be6d4bee99b999e1601de67abc0c0e675c8bb7","tid":1099913,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"公屋兄弟爭公屋房，想殺死自己親細佬"},{"pid":"77afa6917cf231b30717c3dd94014710cdd7ec9b","tid":1099913,"uid":217605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:01:03.000Z","msg":"Sasuke!!!!"},{"pid":"40b1960c182de4ad9f1812f8cc878194d2e5e57b","tid":1099913,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"兄弟 也是無情"}]}